OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,FThe cost of renting and maintaining
OL,7,FDartmoor Prison over the next decade
OL,8,Fcould be up to #100 million, despite
OL,9,Fthe government not being able to
OL,10,Fconfirm if it will ever house
OL,11,Fprisoners again, according to a
OL,12,Fcommittee of MPs.
OL,14,FThe Ministry of Justice has also
OL,15,Fadmitted that it renewed the prison
OL,16,Flease in March 2022, despite knowing
OL,17,Fthere was "a risk" caused by the
OL,18,Fpresence of the radioactive gas.
