OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,FDartmoor Prison has been closed to
OL,7,Finmates since July 2024, due to high
OL,8,Flevels of radon gas, but the MoJ said
OL,9,Fthe "unacceptable" levels were only
OL,10,Fdetected after the lease was renewed
OL,11,Ftwo years earlier.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
