OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,F"Based on the surveys we did before
OL,7,Fand the mitigations that we had taken,
OL,8,Fthe information that we had available
OL,9,Fto us at that time suggested that it
OL,10,Fwould be sensible to keep Dartmoor
OL,11,Fopen, given the pressure on prison
OL,12,Fplaces," the Permanent Secretary to
OL,13,Fthe Ministry of Justice, Jo Farrar,
OL,14,Ftold the Public Accounts Committee
OL,15,F(PAC).
OL,17,FThe cost to the taxpayer of renting
OL,18,Fthe jail is #1.5 million a year, with
OL,19,Fbusiness rates totalling #299,000. But
OL,20,Fthere are other expenses involved too,
OL,21,Finvolving maintenance and security.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
