OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown,
OL,7,FConservative MP and PAC Chair,
OL,8,Festimates the financial cost of
OL,9,Fkeeping it open for another decade -
OL,10,Fif it doesn't house inmates - would be
OL,11,Faround #100 million.
OL,13,FResponding to interrogation by a cross-
OL,14,Fparty group of MPs, Ms Farrar said the
OL,15,F"ambition is still to reopen Dartmoor,
OL,16,Fbecause it provides 640 valuable
OL,17,Fspaces", but was unable to verify the
OL,18,F#100 million estimate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
