OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,F"When the lease was entered into, they
OL,7,Fwere seen to be reasonable and good
OL,8,Fvalue for money," she added.
OL,10,F"We have good ongoing relationships
OL,11,Fwith the Duchy, as you can see by the
OL,12,Freasonably favourable terms of the
OL,13,Flease. The current lease expires in
OL,14,F2048, but we can exit from 2033 on
OL,15,Ffive years' prior notice."
