OL,3,CMPs warn empty Dartmoor prison could
OL,4,Ccost taxpayers #100m over next decade
OL,6,FThe MoJ is now waiting for
OL,7,Frecommendations on radon from the
OL,8,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,9,Fbefore deciding on the future of the
OL,10,Fprison, which is one of the world's
OL,11,Ffamous and most notorious.
OL,13,FThe prison population in England and
OL,14,FWales has risen significantly over
OL,15,Frecent decades, with Labour ministers
OL,16,Fagreeing to release some prisoners
OL,17,Fearly last year in a bid to free up
OL,18,Fcapacity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
